                            "aonid": 59
                        }
                    ],
                    "effect": "The sword emits a 20-foot-radius emanation of holy fire centered on your target, inflicting 2d8 spirit damage and 2d8 vitality damage to all enemies in the area (DC 34 basic Reflex save). Creatures that fail the save are blinded for 1 round, and those that critically fail are blinded for 1 minute.",
